                           Project 2 - An HDL File
                           ----------------------- 
  

Submitted Files
---------------
README - This file.
Add16.hdl - add two 16 bit numbers.
ALU.hdl - arithmetic logic unit.
FullAdder.hdl - add two bits with carry.
HalfAdder.hdl - add two bits with no consideration to carry input. 
Inc16.hdl - incremet number by 1.
Mul.hdl - multiply two numbers.
Or16Way.hdl - helper gate, preform or operation on 16 bits.
ShiftLeft.hdl - shift binary number one cell to the left.
ShiftRight.hdl - shift binary number one cell to the right.

Remarks
-------
* added the Or16Way chip because it seemed to be more elegent.
